                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860531-38-off213 t17860531-38-cd214"></join>, one piece of ivory, value 16 s. another piece, value 1 s. 4 d. another piece, value 1 s. 9 d. another piece, value 9 s. 9 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
