             sworn.</p>
               <p>The prisoner confessed taking my ivory, and he told me that was the first he had ever<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178605310064"></xptr> taken from me; I told him he was a <rs id="t17860531-38-deflabel215" type="occupation">servant</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860531-38-defend512 t17860531-38-deflabel215"></join> I had put a deal of trust and confidence in, and there was no doubt but he had robbed me exceedingly; he was continually in our house; he confessed taking them on the Wednesday.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17860531-38-person518">
                  JAMES
                   WOODLAND
               <interp inst="t17860531-38-person518" type="surname" value="WOODLAND"></interp>
