                     <interp inst="t17860531-38-person518" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am journeyman to the prosecutors, they are in partnership; I am employed to saw their ivory; I swear to one of the pieces of ivory.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17860531-38-person519">
                  JOSEPH
                   SMITH
